<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="358 - 374" refId="ref51024" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2020 b) Taxonomy of Ecuadorian water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817 (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4790 (2), 358 - 374. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4790.2.10" type="journal article" year="2020">Perkins, 2020b</bibRefCitation>
